sentences: Edward Janney is an American musician, producer and artist who has played guitar for many Washington, D.C.-based hardcore punk bands such as Untouchables, The Faith, Rites of Spring, One Last Wish, Happy Go Licky, Skewbald/Grand Union and Brief Weeds, as well as having produced albums for Scream and Embrace and created album covers for Funeral Oration, Monorchid, Rites of Spring and Happy Go Licky.
